overview: Maya Bijou has no money for rent, but she's willing to make other arrangements.  Carmen Caliente: She doesn't want to work to pay rent, but she's eager to pay in other ways.  Carolina Sweets: When you look as good as Carolina does, you don't have to pay with cash.  Gina Valentina: Since she violated the rules, she decides to make it up to her roomate.
tagline: You can sign the agreement or we can make "other arrangements!"
title: Seeking Rental Arrangement 2
